z=a+ib
\frac{z+i}{z-3i}=\frac{a+i(b+1)}{a+i(b-3)}=\frac{[a+i(b+1)][a-i(b-3)]}{a^2+(b-3)^2}
\displaystyle a^2+(b-3)(b+1)=0\iff a^2+(b-1)^2=2^2
